{"tid":760151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉穎結婚 老死自費飛峇里觀禮","createTime":"2018-07-29T09:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T16:19:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a302d8254f37eeeddcdeeea4c5e3040b2a22fee","tid":760151,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】陳凱琳已公開承認與鄭嘉穎的婚訊，盛傳兩人將於8月12日在印尼峇里島舉行婚禮，有指嘉穎希望婚禮低調且順利舉行，下令一眾出席賓客封口，不可透露婚禮確實地點及時間。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指鄭嘉穎年前主演的劇集《鐵馬尋橋》一班好兄弟姊妹如馬國明、黃嘉樂、林子善及唐詩詠等，都會到峇里見證婚禮。另外，有指陳淑芬、曹永廉、唐文龍、黃智賢及賴慰玲等亦獲邀出席。他們都是自費到峇里觀禮，大隊將於8月11日啟程。而即將到峇里參加嘉穎婚禮的藝人朋友，談到此事時都三緘其口，為對方保守秘密，認真夠晒老友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/weetEWnggmCqSb2bQH3eDA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D02d_enp01p06290718copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FweetEWnggmCqSb2bQH3eDA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD02d_enp01p06290718copy.jpg&h=3c855540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%98%89%E7%A9%8E%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E8%80%81%E6%AD%BB%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BB%E9%A3%9B%E5%B3%87%E9%87%8C%E8%A7%80%E7%A6%AE-220519852.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2598%2589%25E7%25A9%258E%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25A9%259A%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E9%25A3%259B%25E5%25B3%2587%25E9%2587%258C%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%25A6%25AE-220519852.html&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2030b6b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%98%89%E7%A9%8E%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E8%80%81%E6%AD%BB%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BB%E9%A3%9B%E5%B3%87%E9%87%8C%E8%A7%80%E7%A6%AE-220519852.html</a>"},{"pid":"da2c22e59d111c706224f1ff1f37a6e1781617f6","tid":760151,"uid":62822,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:29:32.